content: Well i am a shell fanatic i tried to identify 2 different shells and the app wasnt even close..dont get this app absolutely a waste of your 2 bucks..the shells that i tried to identify were whole no broken shells,that i already knew the name of them just wanted to see if the app was legit... and its not! Find a different app!
Its unfortunate that this app was not able to identify over six different types of common cowries.
Good start to this app, but I would like to see more shells that haven't been added yet. Will be happy to upgrade rating later... this is a great idea!
